      "upgrade_patterns": "None observed. Both contracts are constructed via constructors and do not use Initializable/UUPS/Transparent/Beacon/Diamond patterns.",
      "access_control_structure": "Role split between Ownable owner and a dedicated manager in HypoVault: owner can rotate manager/accountant/feeWallet; manager can execute arbitrary calls from the vault and advance/fulfill/cancel epochs. PanopticVaultAccountant uses Ownable to gate pool configuration (pools hash) and locking per vault."
